Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:39.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス暦３１７年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.103,46.4)}"Maryam"\N"Pars"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When their ally, Maryam,\Nwas invaded by the Lusitanian army,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:43.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,友邦マルヤム国に侵攻したルシタニア軍に対し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pars responded on this day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:48.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この日　パルスは国王アンドラゴラス三世の指揮の下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,by meeting them with a force 300,000 strong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,under the command of their king,\NAndragoras Ill, and crushed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,３０万の軍勢で迎え撃ち　撃破
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They built a mountain of\Nthe Lusitanian troops' corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニア兵の屍の山を築き上げた
