Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:38.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　もう一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, above!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:42.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, above!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:43.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, below!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, above!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You are terrible, Vahriz.\NUsing a maneuver like that on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどいな　ヴァフリーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな技を使うなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:04.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この程度のものは技とは申しませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Such trifling moves would\Nnot be considered a maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They were merely fundamental sword strokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの　剣の基本動作です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you do not\Ncultivate those fundamentals,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:13.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし　その基本を鍛えなければ　技も威力を失います
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,your maneuvers will be less powerful as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hone those fundamentals, Prince Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:18.89,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,基本をお磨きなさいませ　アルスラーン殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:22.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,つまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you not accompany my lord\Nfather on his campaign, Vahriz?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:27.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　ヴァフリーズは父上の遠征に同行しなかったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Safeguarding this place,\Nthe Royal Capital of Ec—batana,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:31.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ　王都エクバターナの守護が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is the duty that I have been\Nassigned upon this occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,此度　私に与えられた任務です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192.901,49.6)}"Supreme General, Kingdom of Pars\NVahriz"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not only Lusitania to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,西のルシタニアのみならず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192.901,49.6)}"Supreme General, Kingdom of Pars\NVahriz"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kingdoms to the east have\Ntheir eyes upon this city as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,東方の国々もこの都を狙っておりますゆえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so we mustn't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,油断はなりませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are so busy, you needn't\Ngive me daily sword lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに忙しいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:48.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,毎日　私に　剣の稽古など　つけてくれなくてもよいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking with such lackluster ambition,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そのような覇気のないことをおっしゃられていては
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you will never become a fine king.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,立派な王にはなれませぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even simply mastering the\Nfundamentals of the sword
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,剣の基本ができているだけでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,will show in how you carry\Nyourself straight and tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,立ち居振る舞いがしゃんとして見えるものです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have yet to embark\Nupon your maiden battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それに殿下は　初陣もまだですから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so you must practice the sword\Nin preparation for that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.95,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その日に備えて剣を鍛えておきませんと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっているけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know it, then look sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:18.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっておられるなら　きりっとなさいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers are waiting as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,兵たちも待っております
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your service does you great credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大儀である
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(188.094,47.2)}"Queen, Kingdom of Pars\NTahamenay"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope for much to come of\Nyour eternal allegiance to Pars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:39.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,永遠なるパルスへの忠誠を期待します
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To Her Majesty the Queen\Nand Prince Arslan! Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王妃様とアルスラーン殿下に敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:51.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,母上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Arslan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんです　アルスラーン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:58.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ　いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:01.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お待たせして　申し訳ありませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It seems you\Npractice the sword every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:05.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いいえ　毎日剣の稽古をしているそうですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,は…はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I {\i1}am{\i} working hard in order to\Nbecome a fine king like my lord father,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:11.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上のような立派な王になるために励んではいるのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but my progress has been slow.\NVahriz is always--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか上達いたしません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも　ヴァフリーズに…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to become a fine king?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,立派な王になるとは　何なんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Azrael!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アズライール　スルーシ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Soroush!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! If they have returned, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:43.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ほう　こやつらが帰って来たということは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おいで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:48.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Azrael.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.73,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おかえり　アズライール
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:53.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lord Vahriz. I trust I find you unchanged?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァフリーズ殿も　お変わりありませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishward, you have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,キシュワード　戻ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, upon their return, they greet not\Ntheir master, but Your Highness first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,飼い主より先に殿下に帰還の挨拶とは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The cheeky bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,生意気なヤツらめ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no respect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なめられているな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(185.69,41.6)}"Cavalry Captain, Kingdom of Pars\NKishward"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it is not that they do not respect me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:12.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いえいえ　私がなめられているのではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(185.69,41.6)}"Cavalry Captain, Kingdom of Pars\NKishward"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but that they hold the deepest\Naffection for His Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:16.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらが心の底から　殿下を慕っているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:21.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,獣や鳥は相対する人物の心を映す鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Birds and beasts are mirrors
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that reflect what is in the heart of\Nthose they come face-to-face with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They know the soundness of\NHis Highness's heart and mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:26.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下の心の健やかさをこやつらは分かっているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:31.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,遠征　ご苦労であった　皆　無事か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your service on the campaign\Nis appreciated. All are safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ　当方の損害は軽微にて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our losses were negligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Pars forces crushed the Lusitanian army
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,友邦マルヤムに侵入したルシタニア軍を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that invaded our ally Maryam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.32,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我がパルス軍が撃退いたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty, King Andragoras, is returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドラゴラス陛下のご帰還です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(203.117,48.8)}"Cavalry Captain, Kingdom of Pars\NKharlan"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Marzbān Kharlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,マルズバーン・カーラーン様
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(203.117,48.8)}"Cavalry Captain, Kingdom of Pars\NKharlan"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--How gallant!\N--Lord Kharlan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.09,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,かっこいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:03.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,カーラーン様
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(203.117,48.8)}"Cavalry Captain, Kingdom of Pars\NKharlan"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The one over there is Lord Marzbān Kubard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あっちはマルズバーン・クバード様だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(203.117,48.8)}"Cavalry Captain, Kingdom of Pars\NKharlan"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's drinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:08.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,また　酒飲んでるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he {\i1}ever{\i0} sober?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人　シラフのときあんの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:15.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってる　あの左目の傷は竜と戦ったとき　付いたんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That scar over his left eye is\Nfrom when he fought a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,うそつけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite is still Lord\NTwin-Blade General Kishward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:20.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　やっぱり双刀将軍キシュワード様だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'm going\Nto join the cavalry, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:25.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大きくなったら俺も騎兵隊に入って　王様をお守りするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to protect the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy! Like the king\Nneeds anyone to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:29.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,バ～カ　王様がお守りなんか　いるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought down a lion at the age of thirteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,１３歳で獅子を倒してるんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prisoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:35.58,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,捕虜か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Lusitanian soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニア兵だわ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones who fight for their god, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:40.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,神のために戦うってやつでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cult of Yaldabaoth, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:43.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,イアルダボート教か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear they kill anyone who doesn't\Nshare their beliefs, even babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:47.03,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,異教徒は　赤子までも皆殺しにするんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How barbaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,野蛮ね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,子供じゃねぇか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lusitania sends even children like that into war?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:55.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな子供まで戦に出すのかい　ルシタニアは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing. What are his parents doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:59.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,かわいそうに　親は何をやってるんだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:05.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Father, I am most gl'ad to see you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:12.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上　ご無事で何よりです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The fighting was off in\Ndistant lands and I worried--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,遠い地での戦で　心配しており…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat was never a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.81,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Vahriz, report to me of the\Ngoings-on during my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ヴァフリーズ　留守中の報告をせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:24.81,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Prince Arslan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:29.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王子は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りないなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to protect him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちが守ってやんなくちゃだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A young one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:47.33,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,若いヤツだ　力仕事できるヤツが欲しいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want one that can do physical labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:48.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My prince, entering too far\Ninto such quarters is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり　このような場所に立ち入られるのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? This is a great opportunity\Nto speak to Lusitanians.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　せっかくルシタニア人と話せる機会ではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you require slaves,\Nwe could send a messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷が必要なのでしたら　使いの者に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wish to hear for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.39,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　自分で聞いてみたいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,About the kingdoms out there.\NOf the people out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,外の国のこと　外の人間のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Do as you're told!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:08.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,このやろう　言うこと聞きやがれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Prince Arslan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,これは　アルスラーン殿下　このようなむさ苦しい所に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you to these shabby quarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these men the ones from Lusitania?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この者たちがルシタニアの？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. If possible, I would\Nlike to speak with you a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こんにちは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:24.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,できれば　少し君たちと話がしたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:27.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ…ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:30.37,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こらっ　なんてことしやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:32.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all slaves now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,てめぇらは　もう奴隷なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to live, do as you're told!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,生きていたけりゃ従え　分かったか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, it's a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　子供だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's not do this after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ　やっぱり　やめようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying? We're here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　今更
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to join the cavalry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:49.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　騎兵隊に入るんだろ　びびってどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you get scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give him a good thrashing,\Nso he'll {\i1}never{\i} defy us Parsians again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.83,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちパルス人に逆らえないように　ガツンとやってやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Such barbaric folk...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな野蛮な連中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If something {\i1}were{\i} to happen to you,\Nthere would {\i1}be{\i} no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王子の身に何かあってからでは遅いのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,lam not stupid, either. I will be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.15,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私もバカではない　気をつけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,た…助け…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王子　お待ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来るな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつを殺すぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is there any chance I\Ncould get you to let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:36.95,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なあ　お主　そやつを放してやってはくれぬか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　だったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ　ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,痛てっ　ちょっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:47.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:50.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‘Wﬁat happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My goods ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,商品が逃げた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:53.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:56.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　いや　逃げただけならいいんだが…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If all he did was run away,\NI wouldn't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王子が…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He protected us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.89,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちをかばって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:02.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,捜せ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.90,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい　何があったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The west side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,西側だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,逃がすな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんの騒ぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:19.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン様
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Prince Arslan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王子が…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,追え
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,痛い…痛っ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:40.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:54.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その方を放せ　もう逃げられんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.74,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,寄るな　寄れば　こいつの首をへし折るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come any closer and I'll break his neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたくなかったら走れ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?!\N--Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.25,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:14.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ　すまぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--My apologies!\N--Run, you slowpoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,走れ　のろま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Arslan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. If this gets\Nreported to the palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:27.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まずいぞ　こんなことが宮殿に伝わったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, which way did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　どっちに行った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よし　急げ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:40.06,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれほどの人数で追ってくるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming after me with that many men...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be the pampered son\Nof a prominent family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様　いいとこの坊ちゃんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I made the right choice\Nswitching hostages to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:46.82,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人質を貴様に代えて　正解だったようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you unharmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大事ないか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You saved m...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,すまない　助かった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this long-necked creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.95,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　この首の長い生き物は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you never‘seen one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,見たことないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The masters of entertainment\Nbring them by all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:24.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,興行師がよく連れてくるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a creature that lives in these parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:28.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この辺りにいる生き物なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea? You're a useless one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,｢さあ｣って　使えないヤツ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--Come!\N--O-Owowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:33.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,来い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.75,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,い…痛てっ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんと豊かな国だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rich kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is overflowing\Nwith people and things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,物と人があふれ返っている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:46.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは大陸公路の中心だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We are at the heart of the\NContinental Highway, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:50.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス人は飢えを知らず　文化的に豊かに暮らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Parsians know no hunger and\Nlead prosperous, cultured lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.24,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,今度はどこに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that! Go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから上がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have a lot of slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:06.19,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷が多いようだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それはそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷の多さは　この国の豊かな証拠だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The large number of slaves is proof\Nof this kingdom's prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.81,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　お主は逃げるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you guietly submit to being a slave,\Nyou will never want for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:18.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おとなしく奴隷になれば　食べるのには困らぬぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,少なくともルシタニアより　よい暮らしができるであろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, you would have\Na better life than back in Lusitania...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと　我が国が貧しいというのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying my kingdom is poor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, when children such as\Nyourself are heading off to war...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:29.45,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああいや　こんな子供が戦に出るほどだから…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no child! I'm eleven years old already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,子供ではない　もう１１歳だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven?! The same as I! You {\i1}are{\i} a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,１１　私と一緒　やはり　子供ではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,By this age, we are full-fledged warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この年になれば　立派な戦士だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We devote ourselves in the\Nservice of the{\i} God of Yaldabaoth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:43.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我らイアルダボート神に忠誠を尽くし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:45.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,異教徒を根絶やしにするのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and we will wipe out the heathens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you so despise\Nthose who do not believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:48.54,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　そこまで異教徒を憎む
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:53.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我らが神は　人を平等に扱う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our god treats all men as equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:56.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　貴様らはどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You place people beneath other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:01.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人の下に人を置く　あの奴隷制度はなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.28,UP JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こらっ　なんにやってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey! What are you doing?!\N--What the hell is this system of slavery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our god will not stand for such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.64,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,我らの神は　そのようなことは許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,人は皆　平等だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All men are equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you heathens,\Nwho do not follow our god's teachings,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:16.66,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よって　我らの神の教えに従わぬ貴様ら異教徒は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,may be treated as different and killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:18.88,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,差別し　殺してもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is utterly illogical.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.47,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,支離滅裂だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:21.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,--You bastard!\N--Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　いや
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.65,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.42,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,また
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,ll people would just embrace the God of Yaldaba
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:36.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての人がイアルダボート神を信仰すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no fighting to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.26,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも争いなど起こらん　分かるか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.12,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ　何も考えずに育ったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably grew up without\Na thought in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn ignorant pampered boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,世間知らずのお坊ちゃんめ　親の顔が見たいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The parents you must have!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:48.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose could be going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでございましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a commotion down below...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,下の方が慌しいようですが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned, Tahamenay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,戻ったぞ　タハミーネ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,留守の間　変わりなかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Has all remained unchanged in my absence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not at least divest yourself of your armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,鎧くらい　お脱ぎになっては
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,土産だ　よい絹が手に入った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I obtained some fine silks--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.79,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか　そこに置いておいてください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I will come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,また来る
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The west rampart! Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:34.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,西の城壁だ　逃がすな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.22,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.49,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,早く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,痛て…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.48,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,寄るな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:54.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,この者が　どうなってもいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want anything\Nto happen to him, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もはや　ここまでか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender yourself. Do not die needlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:04.08,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,投降せよ　無駄死にはするな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.92,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell from up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,上から落ちたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.67,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫かい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.00,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, up we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.71,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そらっ　せぇ～の
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! He...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.41,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.61,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,馬泥棒　おい　待て
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Horse thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:06.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　待て
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,アルスラーン殿下　おケガは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Arslan, are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ダリューン　大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryun, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.86,UP JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　俺の馬　捕まえてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop me from shooting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.31,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　あの者を討つことをお止めになったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:43.71,UP JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着いて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.85,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　つい…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:52.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました　私が討ち損じたことにしておきます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. We will say\Nthat I failed to find my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, thank goodness that he's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.38,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に無事でよかったねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,捕虜に捕まって　振り回されたって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Captured by a prisoner and dragged\Nalong on a wild-goose chase, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:00.07,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,危ねぇなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:18:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is the prince doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:02.43,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,何やってんだか　王子は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be a little more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.99,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し　お気をつけください
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.16,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,一歩間違えば　殺されてましたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One misstep and you could have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.62,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それを言われると…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.02,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Royal Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have captured the three whose\Nactions resulted in the prisoner's escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:20.01,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,捕虜の脱走の原因を作った３名を捕らえてまいりました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--Your Highness!\N--We are so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.68,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.29,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お許しください　殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive them, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,罰なら　私たちに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Punish us instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We beg of you to show leniency\Ntowards our children!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:31.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,子供たちには　何とぞ寛大な処置を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Control yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:32.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,控え
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because of them that\NHis Highness's life was put at risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:37.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつらのせいで　殿下のお命が危険にさらされたのだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is fine. Release them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.78,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,よい　放してやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It would set a bad examp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.40,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ならん　示しが…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.59,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All are safe. That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.29,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,無事なら　それでよい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.44,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:48.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'll join the cavalry,\Nno matter what I have to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:58.09,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺　大きくなったら　絶対騎兵隊に入って　殿下にお仕えします
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to be in your service, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:09.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな　無事でいろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.72,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず助けに戻るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back to rescue you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,馬を持ってまいります
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring you a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The things he had to say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:24.56,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの者の話は　王宮で教えられたものと違って面白かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}were{\i} interesting and different from\Nwhat I have been taught at the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear what the other captive\NLusitanians have to say as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:29.13,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,囚われている他のルシタニア人にも　話を聞きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry up and carry them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:30.50,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと運べ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:34.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:35.76,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お…王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My prince?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.87,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,早くしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.09,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:49.10,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なりません　このような汚らわしい所に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not be here in this filthy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:52.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殺してしまったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:53.30,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They were unruly and there was\Nnothing to be done with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.35,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,暴れてどうにもなりませんでしたので
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lusitanians are the same as animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:59.77,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニア人など　獣と同じです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no taming them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.36,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,飼いならすことはできませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:03.86,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　急げ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Those men...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:15.23,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,あの者たち　素直に奴隷になっておれば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If they had quietly accepted becoming slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,they would not have lost their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.80,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,命を落とさなかったものを…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:21.21,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:27.27,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,殿下　いつか殿下がご即位なされましたら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, when you have\Nascended to the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.60,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,登用していただきたい我が友人がおります
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a friend of mine that\NI would like for you to appoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That man may be able to answer\NYour Highness's questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:36.28,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その者なら　殿下の疑問に答えられるかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,それは誰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:39.84,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　いや
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.98,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,口が滑りました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a thoughtless remark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a crotchety man,\Nso please forget that I said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.37,0:21:46.20,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,そやつはひねくれ者ゆえ　今の話はなかったことに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now you have me wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:49.17,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　思わせぶりな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:56.04,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ　この先　何十年も父上の王位は揺るがぬだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord father's reign is unlikely\Nto waver for many decades to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:22:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot yet even begin to\Nimagine ascending to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:22:00.11,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,私が即位することなど　まだ想像もつかぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as my lord father is here,\Nour kingdom of Pars will be secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:04.34,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,父上がおれば　我がパルスは安泰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it will be a while\Nbefore I get to meet your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.25,0:22:08.51,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,お主の友人とやらには　しばらく会えそうにないな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:10.05,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.91,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　これより３年後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, three years hence,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the Royal Capital of Ecbatana\Nwould be shrouded in fire and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:20.69,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王都エクバターナは　炎と血煙に包まれることとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maryam, their ally kingdom,\Nwould fall before Lusitania's invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.96,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,ルシタニアの侵略により　盟邦マルヤム王国は滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And that onslaught would\Nfinally reach as far as Pars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:30.93,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,その進撃は　ついにパルスにも及んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pars Era, the year 320, autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.57,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,パルス暦３２０年　秋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:39.46,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,王太子アルスラーン　時に１４歳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At the age of fourteen, Crown Prince Arslan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...embarks upon his maiden battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:41.14,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,初陣す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The azure crescent moon\Nwheels across the night sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The glittering world transcends the clouds{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With this journey’s beginning that you dance now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:23:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Off into the yonder wishes go, drifting{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a tale that is shapeless{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spreads across the moonlight{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The treasure that is within you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Melts away into the wind now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow, try to take\Nwing as your unvarnished self{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometime, somewhere,\Nyou wanted this, remember?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can hear it, can ’t you?\NThere, that shining dream from that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The azure crescent moon\Nwheels across the night sky{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The glittering world transcends the clouds{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With this journeyﬁs beginning that you dance now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:24:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Off into the yonder wishes go{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:15.18,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,風が翻り　霧が流れた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.81,0:24:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind changed and the fog rolled in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed an auspicious omen to Arslan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:18.52,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,吉兆であるように　アルスラーンには思えた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.55,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(184.488,50.4)}"Chapter II\NAge Fourteen, Maiden Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, "Age Fourteen, Maiden Battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, the boy would become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.94,TEXT JPO - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL-ja,,0,0,0,,少年は　そして王となる
